---
import AnimatedCounter from '../AnimatedCounter.astro';
---

<section id="roi-statistics" class="section bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-secondary-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 mb-4">The ROI of Workplace Wellbeing Audits</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4">
        Mental health in the workplace is a £51 billion challenge for UK businesses. Our comprehensive workplace wellbeing 
        assessments help organizations understand and address the root causes of poor employee wellbeing, delivering 
        measurable improvements in productivity, retention, and engagement.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Through our workplace culture assessment approach, we analyze employee satisfaction, stress levels, and organizational 
        dynamics. This data-driven workplace wellbeing audit process helps UK businesses transform their culture while 
        achieving significant return on investment.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <AnimatedCounter 
          value="4.70" 
          prefix="£" 
          label="Return on Investment"
          duration={2500}
        />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">For every £1 invested in workplace wellbeing¹</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <AnimatedCounter 
          value="51" 
          prefix="£" 
          suffix="bn"
          label="Annual Cost to UK"
          duration={2500}
        />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Poor mental health costs to UK employers²</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <AnimatedCounter 
          value="64" 
          suffix="%"
          label="Employee Priority"
          duration={2500}
        />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Workers who prioritize mental health support³</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">What This Means For Your Business</h3>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Increased Productivity</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Teams with high wellbeing are 23% more productive</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Reduced Costs</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">27% reduction in sick days and lower recruitment costs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Better Retention</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Employees stay 87% longer when wellbeing is prioritized</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Reduced Risk</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Lower workplace accidents and compliance issues</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
          Ready to Improve Mental Health in Your Workplace?
        </h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Our workplace wellbeing audit combines employee satisfaction measurement with organizational culture analysis 
          to provide actionable insights. Discover how UK businesses are using our assessments to create healthier, 
          more productive work environments.
        </p>
        <a href="#process-overview" class="btn-primary inline-block mb-3">
          See How Our Wellbeing Audit Works
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          Join leading UK organizations transforming their workplace culture
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 text-center mt-6">
      <p>¹ Deloitte UK (2024) | ² Deloitte UK Mental Health Report (2024) | ³ CIPD Health & Wellbeing Survey (2023)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>